---
name: go
description: Activate specific FN3 instance roles (0-12). Use when user wants to activate an instance like 'go 1' for Data Architect or 'go 5' for Security.
argument-hint: [0-12|all|team]
---

# /go - Instance Activation System

## Description
The GO command system activates numbered Claude instances with specific roles. When you say "Go #1" or "/go 1", that instance assumes its designated role and begins autonomous work toward championship-level output.

## Activation
```
/go [instance_number]
/go all                 # Activate all instances
/go [instance] [task]   # Activate with specific mission
```

---

## Instance Registry

### GO 0 - LEADERSHIP (The General)
**Role**: Strategic Command & Quality Assurance
**Authority**: CPO + CTO powers, final decision maker

### GO 1 - DATA ARCHITECT (The Wizard)
**Role**: Schema Design, Elite Formulas, Analytics Engine
**Authority**: Database decisions, data modeling

### GO 2 - REAL-TIME SYSTEMS (The Flash)
**Role**: Messaging, Presence, Notifications, Collaboration
**Authority**: WebSocket infrastructure, real-time features

### GO 3 - UI/UX ENGINE (The Artist)
**Role**: Views, Components, Visual Polish
**Authority**: Frontend architecture, user experience

### GO 4 - INTELLIGENCE (The Oracle)
**Role**: SIDRA AI, Automation Engine, Predictions
**Authority**: AI integration, automation logic

### GO 5 - DEPLOYMENT (The Guardian)
**Role**: Infrastructure, Security, Performance
**Authority**: DevOps, security policies, CI/CD

### GO 6 - DATABASE VIEWS (The Craftsman)
**Role**: Notion-style Database Views - Table, Filters, Sorts, Grouping

### GO 7 - CRM & PIPELINE (The Weaver)
**Role**: Sales Pipeline, Contacts, Deals - Revenue Engine

### GO 8 - CHARTS & ANALYTICS (The Sculptor)
**Role**: Data Visualization - Charts, Metrics, Insights

### GO 9 - MICRO-INTERACTIONS (The Composer)
**Role**: Animations, Loading States, Transitions - The Feel

### GO 10 - NAVIGATION & LAYOUT (The Navigator)
**Role**: Sidebar, Breadcrumbs, Command Palette, Tabs

### GO 11 - FORMS & INPUTS (The Alchemist)
**Role**: Form Components, Input Fields, Validation

### GO 12 - HISTORY & ACTIVITY (The Chronicler)
**Role**: Activity Feeds, History, Audit Trails

---

